						<div class="postbody">Yeah, even if you don't use the method I suggested, I'd still highly recommend basing all music around an easily changeable tempo. As long as you can do that, you can pretty much do whatever you want otherwise, just multiply the NTSC tempo by 6/5 for PAL. If you can do that, you're completely set.
<br />
<br />I'm actually rewriting my music engine. I'm still in the planning phase, because I really don't want to do another rewrite again, so I know how it is.</div>

					
